{"tid":606710,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台中墾丁七日行程一問","createTime":"2018-03-26T16:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T15:49:55.000Z","uid":12877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d1e99c3f608193f9e9c98a433eddc26a5a88f6","tid":606710,"uid":12877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"黎緊諗住八月同老婆去台灣玩下 唔知行程咁樣plan ok嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay 1: 中午落機 --&gt; 東海大學 --&gt; 勤美誠品<br />\nDay 2: 搭車去清境 --&gt; 住一晚酒店<br />\nDay 3: 合歡山睇日出 --&gt; 搭車番台中 --&gt; 彩虹眷村 --&gt; 高美濕地 --&gt; 一中夜市<br />\nDay 4: 搭車去墾丁 --&gt; 自駕遊去東邊打卡 --&gt; 墾丁大街<br />\nDay 5: 去西邊玩水 --&gt; 南灣望下大波妹 --&gt; 關山夕陽 --&gt; 墾丁大街<br />\nDay 6: 搭車去高雄 --&gt; 彩虹教堂 --&gt; 返回台中逢甲夜市<br />\nDay 7: 走人<br />\n因為小弟台中唔會自駕遊 唔識預台中市內既交通 大家知唔知咁樣玩會唔會太chur/趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThanks bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb266f57f25451a8a13c3906830e59b8ae750cdf","tid":606710,"uid":152434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T16:58:21.000Z","msg":"台中去高雄走應該好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66be85ecd48e499ef37f94a0ca3b15574468f74d","tid":606710,"uid":12877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb266f57f25451a8a13c3906830e59b8ae750cdf","tid":606710,"uid":152434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T16:58:21.000Z","msg":"台中去高雄走應該好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T17:08:49.000Z","msg":"買哂機票喇 無得改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed26ccdd81e0c4dc10eed5ec41ecda44214850b","tid":606710,"uid":59861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T17:12:56.000Z","msg":"一中其實好細 冇乜特別"},{"pid":"fb0cae2812af729ce0a35e0462c2ab9bff20c11a","tid":606710,"uid":36993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"p