 入夜難等車 的士會坐地起價<br />\n日落幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/012504_ad000653bc60c4efee9bfc33e708392c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F012504_ad000653bc60c4efee9bfc33e708392c.png&h=8192efdd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"accc439f0370a476644afb1b41b3c866a3750b90","tid":606710,"uid":140481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T17:30:37.000Z","msg":"我想問下台灣旅行嘅時候容唔容易搵廁所？同埋係坐式定蹲式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54dcc645d12dce11f23195f84568c30aa9ab022","tid":606710,"uid":164559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T17:34:12.000Z","msg":"第二日成日去清境農場?"},{"pid":"216eac1deec99b12b8a43531f7c933e5390de313","tid":606710,"uid":12877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f54dcc645d12dce11f23195f84568c30aa9ab022","tid":606710,"uid":164559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T17:34:12.000Z","msg":"第二日成日去清境農場?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T23:26:27.000Z","msg":"係 諗住夜晚留一日 第日朝早報日出團<br />\n係咪留唔到咁耐 洗唔洗朝早攝個景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8602d2466ce9b8cd5c6849830a17a0ae4323660a","tid":606710,"uid":12877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c784bb6daa798e5791928eed87d60f5d8234be56","tid":606710,"uid":125436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"台中落墾丁都要成5-6個鐘 同一日想自駕去東邊 可能要朝早早啲出發落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:15:45.000Z","msg":"我諗住搭高鐵係高雄轉車 車程加埋around 三個鐘 不過都諗住要早起身 係唔知朝早台中火車站去高鐵站既交通方唔方便"},{"pid":"6546a0050bbf99ee03b8afe90529113743a7a11c","tid":606710,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDay 4: 搭車去墾丁 --&gt; 自駕遊去東邊打卡 --&gt; 墾丁大街<br />\nDay 5: 去西邊玩水 --&gt; 南灣望下大波妹 --&gt; 關山夕陽 --&gt; 墾丁大街<br />\nDay 6: 搭車去高雄 <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n墾丁大街係一個長長嘅夜市，飲食為主，可以hea到好夜都得。用佢做夜晚聚腳就得。<br />\n日頭你就行你要嘅行程就得。<br />\n你自駕應該可以去到比較多景點，睇返墾丁個地圖順路渣，盡量唔抄小路應該都簡單。"},{"pid":"da97d430915248552d17a769300cb819b196caad","tid":606710,"uid":164559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第二日成日去清境農場?</blockquote>係 諗住夜晚留一日 第日朝早報日出團<br />\n係咪留唔到咁耐 洗唔洗朝早攝個景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該 唔使留咁耐 因為我之前去過一次<br />\n果度得羊同 一片草地我同班朋友係果度 逗留咗一陣就走咗"},{"pid":"228cb2e0bd926ed258c25c3c78316fcf54ca27c7","tid":606710,"uid":33659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da97d430915248552d17a769300cb819b196caad","tid":606710,"uid":164559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第二日成日去清境農場?</blockquote>係 諗住夜晚留一日 第日朝早報日出團<br />\n係咪留唔到咁耐 洗唔洗朝早攝個景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該 唔使留咁耐 因為我之前去過一次<br />\n果度得羊同 一片草地我同班朋友係果度 逗留咗一陣就走咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"清境玩到一日喎<br />\n住一晚凌晨報果個紅色巴士團睇星+日出<br />\n好彩既話可以睇到銀河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d590530f58f972e8b91795b2c830c3c7c68f91e1","tid":606710,"uid":2394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n6月會高雄加墾丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf261ab3f1d1608fe1a5190552b8e2097fb043d7","tid":606710,"uid":140481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"accc439f0370a476644afb1b41b3c866a3750b90","tid":606710,"uid":140481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T17:30:37.000Z","msg":"我想問下台灣旅行嘅時候容唔容易搵廁所？同埋係坐式定蹲式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:14:25.000Z